=== Enshrined deity ===
* {{ill|lt=Kumano Kusubi-no-Mikoto|UNKNOWN|lt=Kumano Kusubi-no-Mikoto}}

=== History ===
It is said to have been moved into Harifu Shrine's precinct by residents of Kumano-yama in the Tenshō era. Until early Meiji, a Kumano festival was held on June 6 with Noh performances.

=== Festival ===
* Annual festival: April 20

