=== Enshrined deities ===
* {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Izanagi-no-Mikoto|1=Izanagi|qid=Q813858}}
* {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Izanami-no-Mikoto|1=Izanami|qid=Q682306}}

=== History ===
Shrine tradition says it was rebuilt in Kōnin 14. In old times it was called '''Hakusan-gū''', but in Meiji it changed to the present name. In Meiji 9 it was ranked village shrine.

=== Festival ===
* Annual festival: May 1

