=== Enshrined deity ===
* {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Kumano Kusubi-no-Mikoto|1=UNKNOWN}}

=== History ===
It formerly stood in Nishino village and was moved to the current location in the Eishō era.

It is currently outside animal-damage-prevention fencing, so ordinary worship is generally not possible.

=== Festival ===
* Annual festival: April 29

